snippet.title: Asphalt 7: Heat - Google Play Game Trailer
snippet.description: Hit the speed of heat in the fastest, most visually stunning edition of the Asphalt series. It's you against the world in 60 of the most amazing cars by prestigious makers like Audi, Lamborghini, Aston Martin & more!
